        <section class="answer_question">
        <div class="common-questions_header"> How to log in to my account</div>
       
            <ol>
                <li>Enter the email address and password associated with your membership and then select Log in with email.</li>
                <li>If you are having trouble logging in, follow the prompts on the <strong>Forgot your password?</strong> link</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section class="answer_question">
        <div class="common-questions_header"> How to log out of my account</div>
        
            <ol>
                <li>To log out of the NCPAC site, select your profile icon from the top right corner of the screen.</li>
                <li>Select <strong>Logout</strong> from the bottom of the menu.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

