        <div class="questions_title" id="meeting_info">Meetings</div>
        <section class="answer_question">
        <div class="common-questions_header" id="meeting_info"> View Meetings and Minutes</div>
       
            <p>You can see all of the meetings that you have attended for each committee when you are logged into your account.</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Clicking on the <strong>Meetings</strong> button</li>
                <li>Select on <strong>Details</strong> to access the minutes, review notes and action items.</li>
            </ol> 
        </section>
        
        <div class="common-questions_header" id="meeting_info"> Download Meeting Minutes</div>
        <section class="answer_question">
            <p>You can download meeting minutes from the Meetings page</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click on the <strong>Details</strong> link.</li>
                    <li>On the<strong> Meeting Details</strong> page, select the underlined minutes to download them for your review.</li>
                </ol>
        </section>

        <div class="questions_title" id="ActionItems"> Action Items</div>
        <section class="answer_question">
        <div class="common-questions_header" id="ActionItems"> View Action Items</div>
        
            <p>All of the Action Items assigned to each member can be viewed and managed on the Action Items page. Here one can check of whether the Item has been completed</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Under the Actions column select <strong>Edit Details</strong> to add notes to the Action Item</li>
                <li>Selecting <strong>Full Details</strong> allows you to check all of the Action Items Details</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
